(462, NULL, 92, 1, '<p>If \\(f(x)=x^2-2 x\\) and \\(g(x)=2 x+1\\), which of the following is a correct expression for \\(f(g(x))\\) ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[1 mark]</p>', 'Quiz', 5, 7, 29, '<p>Solution: $$ \\begin{aligned} f(g(x) &amp; =(g(x))^2-2 g(x) \\\\ &amp; =(2 x+1)^2-2(2 x+1) \\\\ &amp; =4 x^2+4 x+1-4 x-2 \\\\ &amp; =4 x^2-1 \\end{aligned} $$</p>', 'correct', '<p>\\(4x^2-1\\)</p>', '60', 'Easy', '1', 1, NULL, '2024-03-24 18:56:32', '2024-03-24 18:56:32'),
